                    "doc": "Name of the watercourse / stream the station observes (Czech: 'tok'). Sourced by the bridge from the station catalog and propagated to telemetry so consumers can route by river without a separate catalog join."
                  },
                  {
                    "name": "water_level",
                    "type": [
                      "null",
